content: Welcome to Connectathon 27. We will use this topic for chat during the Connectathon, 5/17-19/2021.
Hello! We are looking to partner with any CBRO, Smart App or EHR entity for the SDOH Connectathon! Thanks-Karen Iapoce-ZeOmega
Is there a track signup document yet?
